                      "issue": null,
                      "page": null,
                      "version": null,
                      "material_number": null
                    },
                    "date": 1990
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The cross section of",
                "monitor reaction was determined by interpolation of the",
                "evaluated values of the reference."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " An effective deuteron beam energy of 125 keV",
                "and beam current of 200 uA were used to produce",
                "neutrons. And the tritium-titanium (T-Ti) target used",
                "in the generator was 2.40 mg/cm2 thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Total uncertainty of cross section is in the",
                "range from 10% to 20%. The uncertainties resulted from",
                "counting statistics, standard cross sections",
                "uncertainties, detector efficiency, weight of samples,",
                "self-absorption of gamma-rays and the coincidence sum",
                "effect of cascade gamma-rays."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The neutron flux was monitored by a uranium fission",
                "chamber so that corrections were made for small",
                "variations in the yield. The self-absorption of the",
                "sample at a given gamma-energy, the coincidence sum",
                "effect of cascade gamma-rays in the investigated",
                "nuclide and in the counting geometry were taken into",
                "account in data analysis, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "STATUS": [
